parameters: The slime gets deeper here as it leads you down into the tunnel that connects these slime tunnels with the rest of the dungeon. Do you want to head back?

As you are walking along, you encounter another slime person. Its a bit hard to make them out, as they are made of slime, in a slime tunnel, but the darker blue color stands out a bit amidst the greenish slime. You wonder if humanoid Slimes are aggressive, you suppose youll just ask, instead of just blasting them with magic. Actually, can you even cast magic down here? Fire would be an obvious no go, Ice might just get caught in all of this slime, and lightning... well, thatll be the last thing you try down here.
\fiOooo,\fi whats a precious little thing like you doing down here? Are you lost sweetie?
<CC Face: 1>Uh, yeah, I guess I am. Ive got this collar on, so I can wander around down here, but I dont really know where Im going, or anything.

Oh, youve already got a collar? Lets see, oh my, Nimh finally got one? Well, good for her. Just take your next right, and then a left, and her room will be at the end of that hallway. Let her know Saiim would be interested in joining in, would you?
<CC Face: 1>Sure, Ill get right on that, I guess.

Well, that was a bit cryptic, but at least youve got directions now. Plus, you didnt have to electrocute yourself, so that went about as well as it couldve. You should go find this Nimh now, you suppose.

You come to a... \fidoor?\fi Entrance? The end of the tunnel basically just has a door shaped area where the wall is replaced by a dark blue looking slime. It doesnt have a door handle though, so you arent sure how it would open. You decide to try knocking on it instead. The slime is harder than it looks, so you are actually able to make some noise by pounding on it.

Instead of opening like, you know, a door, the darker color slime just fades until its the same as the slime you are currently submerged in, allowing the Slime girl who saved you from before to poke her head out.
Oh! W-What are you doing here? Actually, how are you even down here? Werent you drowning in our slime last time I found you?
<CC Face: 1>Yeah, I was, but I put on the collar you left behind, and suddenly I could \fionly\fi breathe slime.
The Slime girl, Nimh you suppose, starts shoving her arms \fiinto\fi her body frantically and wiggling them around, like shes searching for something.
Ah! I really did lose it! What am I going to...
She cuts off, finally looking at your neck, as if just processing the part where you already told her you were wearing the damned thing. Her face turns deep blue as she starts to blush furiously.
<CC Face: 1>Should I have not put it on? Sorry about that, I guess.
Y-Yes, you d-definitely shouldnt have put that on. I mean, its not like I really mind or anything, but...
<CC Face: 1>I have no idea what you are talking about here.
Oh, r-right, you probably cant read whats on the collar, can you? Well, how do I explain this in a way youd understand... It uh, basically tells people that I own you.
O-Or more like my sex slave, maybe?
Well its just so nobody else tries to impregnate you! If you werent wearing it, youd be \fiwell\fi on your way to being a mother, so dont get mad at me!
You are stunned to silence at that, and it takes you a minute to find words once again.
<CC Face: 1>I cant be a mother though.
Well, its not like how you humans do it. We raise our children as a community, youd be less like a mother and more of a... breeding partner, I guess.
Great, so youve been wearing a collar that says Nihms brood mare all around the slime tunnels?
The point being that you wouldnt be expected to raise the children yourself, we take care of our young ourselves.

<CC Face: 1>Im starting to get the feeling that the way you make babies is a lot different from the way we make babies.

Because I really want to knock you up!

You turn to leave, but Nimh lunges forward and grabs you by the arm, before dragging you back into her room and shutting the door.
<CC Face: 1>You know, I dont think this is going to end well, but Im starting to consider trying out lightning magic down here, what do you think?

U-Um, well... \fipleeeeeease\fi let me fuck you!
Nimh wraps her arms around you and starts sobbing into your chest while she begs for you to mate with her. Its sad to watch, honestly. After a little bit, she calms down enough to regain her senses.
